sentence: Procter & Gamble ( PG ) is getting attention Thursday from call buyers.
So far, 14,376 contracts of the July 77 call have changed hands, against open interest of 308 contracts.
Pricing of today's trades has been in the high side of the bid-ask spread, indicating that these new contracts were initiated from the buy side.
IK-> The technicals for PG ($76.37 up $0.52) are neutral with an upward trend.
Look at the Aug. 67.50/70 bull-put spread for a 20-cent credit.
That's an 8.7% return and the stock has to fall by 8.3% to cause a problem.
